{"tid":466834,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"香港地處處都要錢","createTime":"2017-11-13T02:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T03:21:39.000Z","uid":68901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"05e81824e9e28a8db9b3c43def9aaa6c4b756edb","tid":466834,"uid":68901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:56:00.000Z","msg":"無錢就係無錢 同人唔同命<br />\n有d含住金鎖鑰出世 自然唔明係底層既人既苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n撘車有貴 食飯又貴 淨係lunch係街食都要45-50 <br />\n只係想講係香依個地方 窮既只會原地踏步 但有錢既只會繼續有錢 好似炒樓咁 樓價只會越黎越貴 租金都係 莫講話上樓 有首期我都寧願做小生意 免得一世供層樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d344f362546615d5506150a95b97dead41c9b8","tid":466834,"uid":482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:57:05.000Z","msg":"俾你現在有錢你想做咩小生意"},{"pid":"09f4e491870a8d971b2cd5098ae70b08e7ec9a77","tid":466834,"uid":68901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:57:52.000Z","msg":"小弟月入唔多 但自己叫做夠用 可以草到了2500-3000一個月 但真係從來都無諗過買到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76250eaa97bb1b2e831be796203bcc8e258669ce","tid":466834,"uid":68901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:58:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俾你現在有錢你想做咩小生意</blockquote><br />\n會同朋友夾錢開間飲食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36fdc104d329ee02a4507808d966b6142d0426fa","tid":466834,"uid":53172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T02:59:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟月入唔多 但自己叫做夠用 可以草到了2500-3000一個月 但真係從來都無諗過買到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nx2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b08416fbdf6057401435b826ffaab051f19b607","tid":466834,"uid":68901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:01:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>小弟月入唔多 但自己叫做夠用 可以草到了2500-3000一個月 但真係從來都無諗過買到樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nx2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係香港無私樓又無公屋其實死硬 遲早有一日人工唔夠樓租升得快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1bd552f77c189451f8fd902425ebc4a8ace340","tid":466834,"uid":68901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:07:01.000Z","msg":"身邊有朋友本身屋企私樓 有d更加屋企人買咗層比佢地 而我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 叫做大陸有層樓老豆留 但大陸最多值幾十個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 利申19歲"},{"pid":"9b086c0c330ea43ba9cb0a902a3e78ddbae39249","tid":466834,"uid":68901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:08:50.000Z","msg":"求生活安穩無傷無病好了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d290c6d3d3b16fbf71478d15beb5c66cc43e1a","tid":466834,"uid":68901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:14:34.000Z","msg":"想上黎討論下都無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"022fcc133a559bdcd206e159b25dc57272878d92","tid":466834,"uid":1255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:18:16.000Z","msg":"屋企除左空氣 樣樣都係賬單黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n刷牙飲水痾屎廁紙煮野訓教電腦冷氣<br />\n莫講話出街食啦"},{"pid":"d18e4b5dada878ee2dd603d1c613a33a258d5e4a","tid":466834,"uid":68901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T03:21:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企除左空氣 樣樣都係賬單黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n刷牙飲水痾屎廁紙煮野訓教電腦冷氣<br />\n莫